"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-09-parisolympics-nugent-100m-hurdles-final-brown-williams-miss\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"National record holder Ackera Nugent will be Jamaica's sole representative in the final of the Olympic Games 100m hurdles after a brutal semi-final round at Stade de France in Paris on Friday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23, \"end\": 36, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ackera_Nugent\", \"score\": 0.9999999994786322, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ackera Nugent\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ackera_Nugent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ackera_Nugent\"}, {\"begin\": 45, \"end\": 52, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9996878675054082, \"rank\": 0.00026535618194300256, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 176, \"end\": 181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999995006885075, \"rank\": 4.993139877613685e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In what is arguably one of the deepest events in terms of quality in track and field at the Games, the last two World Athletics Championships gold medallists, Tobi Amusan of Nigeria, the world record holder, and Danielle Williams of Jamaica both failed to make it to the medal round.\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danielle_Williams\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7591637759845857e-24, \"text\": \"Danielle Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danielle_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danielle_Williams\"}, {\"begin\": 427, \"end\": 434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9996878675054082, \"rank\": 0.00026535618194300256, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nugent could only muster third in her semi-final heat, in 12.44 seconds (-0.7m /s), and advanced on time as defending champion Jasmine Camacho-Quinn of Puerto Rico won with 12.35 seconds and world leader Masai Russell of the USA placed second with 12.42 seconds to get the two automatic spots.\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 479, \"end\": 485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Nugent\", \"score\": 0.9992839478702884, \"rank\": 0.0006052299052955645, \"text\": \"Nugent\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Nugent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Nugent\"}, {\"begin\": 606, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasmine_Camacho-Quinn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jasmine Camacho-Quinn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasmine_Camacho-Quinn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasmine_Camacho-Quinn\"}, {\"begin\": 631, \"end\": 642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"score\": 0.983274343145972, \"rank\": 0.017002658056022347, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\"}, {\"begin\": 683, \"end\": 688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\", \"score\": 0.9999800061401813, \"rank\": 1.999425958534701e-05, \"text\": \"Masai\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_p